item.title: How do I make myself Admin? [508]
item.dc:creator: @Burnzcanzpwnz Burnzcanzpwnz
item.description:
@Burnzcanzpwnz wrote:

Simple go into your Login.Java and do Ctrl + F and search for the owners name. When you find it delete his/her name put yours in save and compile when you log in you should be admin.
